            </div>
            
            <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap">
                <a class="btn btn-primary" href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}products/aria/`}>What is ARIA?</a>
                <a class="btn btn-ghost" href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}solutions/ai-agent-governance/`}>See governance →</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Governance crisis band -->
    <section class="container reveal-on-scroll" data-section="governance-crisis" style="padding:32px 0 48px">
        <div class="panel-glass" style="padding:32px">
            <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 300px;gap:32px;align-items:start;margin-bottom:24px">
                <div>
                    <div style="display:flex;align-items:start;gap:24px;margin-bottom:24px">
                        <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/icons/medium/warning-alert-80.png`} alt="" style="width:64px;height:64px;flex-shrink:0" />
                        <div style="flex:1">
                            <h2 style="font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,36px);margin:0 0 16px;color:#E8ECFF">The AI Gold Rush created a governance crisis</h2>
                            <p style="color:#B3BCD2;font-size:17px;line-height:1.7;max-width:860px;margin:0">Ungoverned AI drives runaway spend, opens new attack surfaces, and leaves you without a financial‑grade audit. EmpowerNow is the neutral Layer‑2 that puts guardrails on every action.</p>
